1. *Čujte* me dobro, ovo je važno pitanje. (Listen to me carefully, this is an important question.)
2. Čujte se sa mnom kasnije. (*Get in touch* with me later.)
3. *Čujte* šta vam govorim! (Pay *attention* to what I'm saying!)
4. Čujte li muziku koja svira? (Do you *hear* the music playing?)
5. *Čujte* ovu priču! ( *Listen* to this story!)
6. *Čujte* jednu dobru vest! (*Here's* some good news!)
7. *Čujte* ovaj zvuk! (*Listen* to this sound!)
8. *Čujte* me dok pričam! (*Hear* me out while I'm talking!)
9. *Čujte* se sa svojim prijateljima. (*Keep in touch* with your friends.)
10. *Čujte* njegov glas u pozadini. (*Notice* his voice in the background.)

Note: In Serbian, "čujte" can mean "listen", "hear", "get in touch", "pay attention", "keep in touch", and "notice". The translations above attempt to capture the meaning of the word in each context.